{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "萧易人率领一百一十八名浣花精锐前往下关点苍山方向，途经天生桥遭遇权力帮精心布置的伏击。先是假扮商贩的弓弩手和街道陷阱突袭，好汉们应对有序化解危机。随后九天十地十九人魔之一的“暗杀人魔”戚常戚假扮丧子母亲接近萧易人企图行刺，被萧易人识破其破绽后遁地逃逸。接着“佛口神魔”梁消暑假扮丐帮七袋弟子，先示好揭发戚常戚的毒刺博取信任，再趁拍肩之际以“佛手牛毛刺”暗算萧易人。萧易人身穿萧家三宝之一的“金甲铁衣”防住毒刺，更凭借对丐帮规矩的洞察识破梁消暑伪装，将其擒获。与此同时，蛇王少女与老人在苍山石塔上轻松击杀二十四名点苍余孽。浣花精锐抵达石塔后，少女以蛇王身份现身，唐猛与少女正面对阵时徒手抓住灵蛇并将其撕碎，却被老人从背后以青龙子毒蛇偷袭身亡。少女吹响竹箫召唤万蛇围攻，萧易人令九十人组成杀蛇阵抵御蛇群，出动“十年”十人围困蛇王二人。激战之际，一个穿火红袈裟之人出现，声称要替浣花对付蛇王。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“中原弯月刀洗水清是你什么人？！”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不必闪了，她就是洗水清之师妹戚常戚。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“她的暗杀手段高明，技术却不高明。”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“为什么？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“一个母亲失去了孩子，没有理由不找孩子，先找人拼命，而且她还口口声声说孩子已送命，不像做娘的人。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_shan_yi",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳珊一",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“那一定是因为她未曾做过母亲，不知道为人母者的心情。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“要是我，我也不知道。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "“要是你，你只好死了。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "text": "“你也不见得看得出来呀。”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "“总比你眼睛往人家胸脯瞧的好！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "text": "“你说！你说！你这七年八年脸上长不出一条汗毛的东西，我打死你！我打死你！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "“要打么？你够我打？打就打，怕你呀？！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“解开骡车，我们骑骡到怒山。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "梁消暑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“坐不得！”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "text": "“丐帮？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "梁消暑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“萧大侠好。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "text": "“未知阁下有何见教？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "梁消暑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“这骡儿坐不得。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "text": "“为什么？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "梁消暑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“刚才‘暗杀人魔’戚常戚匿于骡马之间，已各在鞍上置下毒刺，如果你刚才坐下去，恐怕再也站不起来了。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "text": "“那倒要感谢你救命之恩了。”",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "梁消暑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“四海之内皆兄弟也。何况见义勇为，是武林中该有的行止，尤其是浣花剑派亦是同道中人。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "text": "“你是谁？”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "梁消暑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我叫梁消暑，外号人称‘佛口神魔’。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“不知萧家老大闯不闯得过戚常戚，梁消暑那一关？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“要是帮主所注意的浣花剑派最具实力的萧易人和最有潜力的萧秋水，以及一百三十四名效死的人，尚过不了梁、戚这关，那是帮主高估他们了。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“你几时见过帮主看错人的？”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“帮主要是看错，也不必如此劳师动众布署了，不过柳五公子还是要戚、梁二位试试。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“正好像我们一样，要是让他们过了这关，还算是权力帮‘八大天王’的人么？”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“‘蛇王’岂有浪得虚名？”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“点苍余孽？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“二十四人。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“我杀十三个。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“我杀十一个，但佟震北在内。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“佟震北是谁？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“林伧夫之师叔。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“那我没话说。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“我们也可以再比一次，等萧家的人来的时候。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“只要浣花的人还能够来。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "梁消暑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“你别动手，你一动手，我即刻走。只要我用脚一跳，遁地就走，像戚常戚一样，你们奈不了我何。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_chang_qi",
      "speaker_name": "戚常戚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们在下关截杀你们有两批人马；第一批败了，我们还有第二批；”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "speaker_name": "梁消暑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们还是可以再拼拼。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "text": "“你想知道我为什么中了你的‘佛手牛毛刺’而不死？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "text": "“你听说过浣花萧家有三宝吧？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "text": "“因为我仅让你刺到我的甲衣上。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_liang_xiao_shu",
      "text": "“因为丐帮的规矩五袋以上的弟子不能乞讨，你装扮成乞丐，为了酷似，又哀又求又乞又讨，所以丐帮没你这种弟子。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“来的是不是名震江湖萧易人萧大侠，还有武林泰斗浣花剑派门下的英雄好汉？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“我是萧易人。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“原来是你。”",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“你等等，我立刻就来。”",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“她是谁？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "“不知道。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“我轻功是不是很好？”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“你是谁？”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“你要知道我是谁？”",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“你是谁？”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“好，我告诉你……”",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“你是蛇王？”",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“萧易人果是萧易人，能避开我‘灵蛇’的人，确实太少了。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "唐猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他又是谁？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_tang_meng",
      "text": "“你又是谁？”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "唐猛",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“我是唐猛，唐门唐猛！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_tang_meng",
      "text": "“原来是蜀中唐门的高手！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "唐猛",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“你想怎样？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_tang_meng",
      "text": "“据悉唐门暗器，天下无敌，不知够不够得上我的灵蛇快毒。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "唐猛",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“你的蛇在哪里？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_tang_meng",
      "text": "“就在袖里。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "唐猛",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“蛇王的蛇只有一条！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_tang_meng",
      "text": "“真正蛇中之王，只有一条。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "唐猛",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“那我就专杀那一条！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他是谁？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "“姊姊你好美！”",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他又是谁？！”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“告诉他我是谁？”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“他是蛇王。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“他又是蛇王？！”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“蛇王本就有两条。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“蛇王本来就够‘蛇’，唐猛听信蛇王的话，就是蛇王‘蛇’了。我说蛇王只有一条，他就信了，一心只对付我，死了也是活该。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“那你们死了也是活该。”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“去！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“帮主的布署呢？那人来了没有？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“帮主派的人，一定会在他该来的时候来到的。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“今天是什么日子？”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“六月初六。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“我们预算他们什么日子到此？”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“最快六月八，就算是神兵，也得在六月七。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“可是他们今天已经来了。”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "text": "“是的，现在已经来了。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“不单是来了，而且已经在塔下了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“到石塔去！”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14
    }
